    description4: "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left\"><ul><li><span>The driver is permitted to send and read S.M.S messages, provided that he does it with care.</span></li><li><span>He is permitted to send S.M.S messages but not to read ones.  </span></li><li><span id=\"correctAnswer0399\">It is absolutely prohibited,  and dangerous.</span></li><li><span>He is permitted to read S.M.S messages but not to send ones.  </span></li></ul><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: right;padding-top: 4px;\"><span>| «C1» | «C» | «D» | «A» | «1» | «В» | </span><span style=\"float: left;\"><button type=\"button\" onclick=\"var correctAnswer=document.getElementById('correctAnswer0399');correctAnswer.style.background='yellow'\">Correct Answer</button></span></div></div>",
