    title2: "0174. How should you conduct yourself at an exit from a premises or from an access road to a house, when you are about to enter or cross the road?",
    link3: "",
    guid: "",
    description4: "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left\"><ul><li><span>Give way to the vehicles that are driving away from you in the road you are about to enter.</span></li><li><span>The rules for giving “right-of-way” in such an exit are identical to those that apply in the case of an intersection.</span></li><li><span>You must give way to vehicles coming from the right only.</span></li><li><span id=\"correctAnswer0174\">Give-way to the approaching vehicles in the road you are about to enter. </span></li></ul><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: right;padding-top: 4px;\"><span>| «C1» | «C» | «D» | «A» | «1» | «В» | </span><span style=\"float: left;\"><button type=\"button\" onclick=\"var correctAnswer=document.getElementById('correctAnswer0174');correctAnswer.style.background='yellow'\">Correct Answer</button></span></div></div>",
