    guid: "",
    description4: "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left\"><ul><li><span id=\"correctAnswer1696\">Slow down while approaching and crossing the bridge.</span></li><li><span>Always cross the bridge at maximum speed to clear the road for vehicles coming from the opposite direction.</span></li><li><span>Always stop before the bridge, for safety reasons, and then cross it quickly.</span></li><li><span>Accelerate when you approach the bridge only.</span></li></ul><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: right;padding-top: 4px;\"><span>| «C1» | «C» | «D» | «A» | «1» | «В» | </span><span style=\"float: left;\"><button type=\"button\" onclick=\"var correctAnswer=document.getElementById('correctAnswer1696');correctAnswer.style.background='yellow'\">Correct Answer</button></span></div></div>",
