    description4: "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left\"><ul><li><span>Proper adjustment of the driver’s seat prevents the occurrence of “blind spots” while driving in reverse. </span></li><li><span>Is performed by the vehicle’s manufacturer during its manufacturing process, and additional adjustment of the seat is not needed. </span></li><li><span id=\"correctAnswer0870\">Allows you to comfortably see the road and to have an easy and non-tiring drive.</span></li><li><span>Is an important action that should be applied during every periodic treatment of the vehicle. </span></li></ul><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: right;padding-top: 4px;\"><span>| «C1» | «C» | «D» | «1» | «В» | </span><span style=\"float: left;\"><button type=\"button\" onclick=\"var correctAnswer=document.getElementById('correctAnswer0870');correctAnswer.style.background='yellow'\">Correct Answer</button></span></div></div>",
